{"tid":823921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"山竹過後深圳「四停」廣州「三停」 香港僅停課","createTime":"2018-09-17T01:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-17T05:03:01.000Z","uid":12367,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"6e4add80e39f116d574ac4f960202ec68727d207","tid":823921,"uid":12367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:57:52.000Z","msg":"香港昨日面對歷來最強大颱風「山竹」的挑戰，蹂躪本港10小時，多處地區包括柴灣、將軍澳、杏花邨及沙田出現海水倒灌，大量樹木倒塌阻塞馬路，有地盤天秤被吹至塌落隔鄰天台，超過362人在風暴中受傷，其中2人命危。不過在受「山竹」影響的地區紛紛宣佈停工、停課的同時，香港僅得教育局宣佈今日停課，但打工仔要照樣上班，令今日交通陷入癱瘓。<br />\n廣州防颱總指揮部昨日發布「全民動員令」，宣佈全市範圍內實行「三停」，即停工、停產、停課。同時指揮部勒令全市各商務部門、商貿企業必須按照「三停」要求，立即執行停市，而全市商業企業、餐廳、門市、檔口等立即停止營業，確保市民的生命安全。<br />\n深圳昨晚亦發出「防颱風防汛緊急動員令」，宣佈啟動全市防颱風和國家防汛應急響應級別Ⅰ級緊急響應。期間，深圳全市範圍內實行「四停」，即停工、停業、停市、停課。<br />\n至於澳門，昨日就宣佈除救災部門等民防架構相關部門，以及駐外代表機構外，政府其餘部門今日關閉，公務人員毋須上班，而中小學、幼稚園和特殊教育學校今日亦全日停課。  <br />\n<br />\n大陸都不如..又話大陸幾冇人性..人地不知幾有人性話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8fbd3d479a01086f4aa606ac41bb117c137a3cc","tid":823921,"uid":45914,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:59:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b80066f0fb5671a7d0276c4b8592d18db33af5ae","tid":823921,"uid":12367,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"f8fbd3d479a01086f4aa606ac41bb117c137a3cc","tid":823921,"uid":45914,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:59:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T01:59:59.000Z","msg":"系...都係黨好"},{"pid":"77956cfc6a9dad83527337da3ff1daacd5b6b6dc","tid":823921,"uid":53466,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:00:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe2f0fd941f953dd6ebb031327f5e99d4f4d50ed","tid":823921,"uid":167828,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:02:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b10789b39e4eb1eb3a7640830937b85e27f57d4","tid":823921,"uid":49853,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:03:22.000Z","msg":"所以話中國大城市永遠超越唔到香港就係咁解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56075a6dcb33f8f28b22c1128772a578f5311a56","tid":823921,"uid":28279,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登仔為咗一日假，自願同大陸接軌，唔反共 lu"},{"pid":"8fc36d555f7a32f80f7865c5f100aca9fa28f9c7","tid":823921,"uid":129739,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:06:03.000Z","msg":"港豬真係勤奴<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇黎他朝世界末日第日都係要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ae9e52160a536387997d18c418c2af4846f9a7","tid":823921,"uid":51121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:10:56.000Z","msg":"香港班既得利益者唔駛理民意真係最無人性。"},{"pid":"0ca57f313d9fab5af822b587e2a916aa4ad05d85","tid":823921,"uid":2959,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:13:19.000Z","msg":"厲害了，我的港"},{"pid":"c274ed8950e46a259116f77740ae042936c40e1d","tid":823921,"uid":2223,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:15:47.000Z","msg":"根本就係局嚟<br />\n想話比香港人知大陸政府為民着想好過香港政府<br />\n<br />\n呃我唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998a412ab1bf667e2a9d347f370a419349bc6df4","tid":823921,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:18:20.000Z","msg":"好可惡!邪惡嘅資本主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b729658468c96d7d84640614db41180693abfcbf","tid":823921,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:18:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"731da7fc8941a567aeaccb8392f56b0f004cccb6","tid":823921,"uid":107671,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T02:18:58.000Z","msg":"你班港豬都有得停呀! waiting for mtr ar"},{"pid":"31e6e7022674b98334d11a386876ab06